quran[27]{c,v,t}:
  37,25,"“Mubeele murie? Shichila shina shimukhoonyananga tawe?”"
  37,26,"Halali olwa lelo belekhulile muno Nyasaye."
  37,27,"Balihengana abeene khubeene mana bachake okhurebana."
  37,28,"Baliboola mbu: “Toto enywe mwakhwitsilanga okhurulila omukhono omulunji.”"
  37,29,"Balibakalusia mbu: “Halali enywe abeene shimwali Abasuubili tawe."
  37,30,"Efwe shikhwali nobunyali khwinywe tawe, halali enywe abeene mwali abakori."
  37,31,"Mana khumalile okhukhoyeshela likhuwa lia Nyasaye wefu Omulesi. Toto efwe khulapila butswa eshinyasio."
  37,32,"Kho khwabakosia eshichila mbu fwesi khwali abakori.”"
  37,33,"Toto abo inyanga eyo balisaanga halala mushinyasio."
  37,34,"Endio nilwa khulikholela Abamabii."
  37,35,"Toto bo olwa baboolelungwa mbu: “Abulaho nyasaye wundi ehale nende Nyasaye”, nibakhola obufuru."
  37,36,"Ne baboolanga mbu: “Toto efwe khuleshe sa abanyasaye befu okhubeela omukaasi wa amashairi wuno, omulalu?”"
  37,37,"Halali ye yetsa khubwatoto, ne nafuchilisania nende Abarumwa."
  37,38,"Toto enywe mulipila eshinyasio eshilulu."
  37,39,"Ne shimulirungwa tawe, halali kalia akamwakholanga."
  37,40,"Halali Abasumba ba Nyasaye abalobole."
  37,41,"Abo nibo balinyoola omukabo omubiishe."
  37,42,"Ebiamo. Nabo balihebwa oluyali."
  37,43,"Mumikunda chomwikulu chobwokholo."
  37,44,"Baliba khubisaala nibahengane."
  37,45,"Balirererwa buli luno nende lulia eshisanda shieshinywebwa shieyisebele."
  37,46,"Eshinywebwa eshilafu, eshimilimili khubalia banywetsanga."
  37,47,"Shibula obubii bwosibwosi, ne shishibameesinjia tawe."
  37,48,"Ne baliba nende Abakhasi balalengangakho abalali abasatsa babu tawe, betsimoni tsindayi muno."
  37,49,"Abakhasi shinga amabuyu kaliindwa obulai muno."
  37,50,"Balilengana abeene khubeene mana bachake okhureebana."
  37,51,"Aliboola omubooli mulala mubo: “Toto esie ndali nende omwitsa."